title: Le Parapheur
description: Le Parapheur is a French startup that offers a digital solution for managing incoming mail and administrative documents. It provides collaborative tools for local governments to handle, organize, and respond to documents efficiently.

title: Coupe des Régions
description: La Coupe des Régions (COC) is a French community-driven event that highlights regional talents in the game Clash of Clans. It organizes competitive tournaments for players from different regions to showcase their skills and represent their territories.
